Ingredients: 
1TBS of Pumpkin Pure , 1 Teaspoon of Honey , 1/2 Teaspoon Turmeric Powder,  1/2 Teaspoon of Aloe Verda water , 1/2 Teaspoon of

3- Leave on for 10-15 minutes

5- Follow up with good Moisturizer.
